div.div:
PRINT OUTPUT:
prototype: int print_output( int token, int board[], int size)
token = 0 -> solution found (success) -> print the board
token = 1-> problem is well posed but alghoritm failed/no solution
token = -1 parse error, wrong argument number
token = -2 1 or more arguments are NaN
token = -3 parse error, wrong constraints
token = -4 memory allocation error
returns token
